description:
Ciara Bravo [Red Band Society, Wayne, Cherry] joins Anna to talk about her recent film Cherry, hanging out with co-star Tom Holland, 16-second memories, helping sick trees or joining a fire watch, sending a text to the wrong person, surviving a long distant relationship, the ghost who came down the stairs to watch SNL and more. Later in the episode Anna welcomes back the founder and clinical director of Growing Self Counseling and Coaching, Dr. Lisa Marie Bobby to offer some qualified advice.

Learn more about Dr. Bobby at www.growingself.com and check out her podcast The Love, Happiness and Success Podcast
